verses.verse: And this is the blessing <S%H1293><s%>, wherewith Moses <S%H4872><s%> the man <S%H376><s%> of God <S%H430><s%> blessed <S%H1288><s%> the children <S%H1121><s%> of Israel <S%H3478><s%> before <S%H6440><s%> his death <S%H4194><s%>.

And he said <S%H559><s%>, Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> came <S%H935><s%> from Sinai <S%H5514><s%>, And rose <S%H2224><s%> from Seir <S%H8165><s%> unto them <S%H3313><s%>; He shined forth from mount <S%H2022><s%> Paran <S%H6290><s%>, And he came <S%H857><s%> from the ten thousands <S%H7233><s%> of holy ones <S%H6944><s%>: At his right hand <S%H3225><s%> was a fiery <S%H799><s%> law for them <S%H1881><s%>.

Yea <S%H637><s%>, he loveth <S%H2245><s%> the people <S%H5971><s%>; All his saints <S%H6918><s%> are in thy hand <S%H3027><s%>: And they sat down <S%H8497><s%> at thy feet <S%H7272><s%>; Every one shall receive <S%H5375><s%> of thy words <S%H1703><s%>.
Moses <S%H4872><s%> commanded <S%H6680><s%> us a law <S%H8451><s%>, An inheritance <S%H4181><s%> for the assembly <S%H6952><s%> of Jacob <S%H3290><s%>.

And he was king <S%H4428><s%> in Jeshurun <S%H3484><s%>, When the heads <S%H7218><s%> of the people <S%H5971><s%> were gathered <S%H622><s%>, All the tribes <S%H7626><s%> of Israel <S%H3478><s%> together <S%H3162><s%>.
Let Reuben <S%H7205><s%> live <S%H2421><s%>, and not die <S%H4191><s%>; Nor let his men <S%H4962><s%> be few <S%H4557><s%>.

And this is the blessing of Judah <S%H3063><s%>: and he said <S%H559><s%>, Hear <S%H8085><s%>, Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, the voice <S%H6963><s%> of Judah <S%H3063><s%>, And bring <S%H935><s%> him in unto his people <S%H5971><s%>. With his hands <S%H3027><s%> he contended <S%H7227><s%> for himself <S%H5828><s%>; And thou shalt be a help against his adversaries <S%H6862><s%>.

And of Levi <S%H3878><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Thy Thummim <S%H8550><s%> and thy Urim <S%H224><s%> are with thy godly <S%H2623><s%> one <S%H376><s%>, Whom thou didst prove <S%H5254><s%> at Massah <S%H4532><s%>, With whom thou didst strive <S%H7378><s%> at the waters <S%H4325><s%> of Meribah <S%H4809><s%>;

Who said <S%H559><s%> of his father <S%H1><s%>, and of his mother <S%H517><s%>, I have not seen <S%H7200><s%> him <S%H5234><s%>; Neither did he acknowledge his brethren <S%H251><s%>, Nor knew <S%H3045><s%> he his own children <S%H1121><s%>: For they have observed <S%H8104><s%> thy word <S%H565><s%>, And keep <S%H5341><s%> thy covenant <S%H1285><s%>.

They shall teach <S%H3384><s%> Jacob <S%H3290><s%> thine ordinances <S%H4941><s%>, And Israel <S%H3478><s%> thy law <S%H8451><s%>: They shall put <S%H7760><s%> incense <S%H6988><s%> before <S%H639><s%> thee <S%H3632><s%>, And whole burnt-offering upon thine altar <S%H4196><s%>.

Bless <S%H1288><s%>, Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, his substance <S%H2428><s%>, And accept <S%H7521><s%> the work <S%H6467><s%> of his hands <S%H3027><s%>: Smite <S%H4272><s%> through the loins <S%H4975><s%> of them that rise <S%H6965><s%> up against him <S%H8130><s%>, And of them that hate him <S%H6965><s%>, that they rise not <S%H4480><s%> again <S%H6965><s%>.

Of Benjamin <S%H1144><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, The beloved <S%H3039><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> shall dwell <S%H7931><s%> in safety <S%H983><s%> by him <S%H2653><s%>; He covereth him all the day <S%H3117><s%> long <S%H7931><s%>, And he dwelleth between his shoulders <S%H3802><s%>.

And of Joseph <S%H3130><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Blessed <S%H1288><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> be his land <S%H776><s%>, For the precious things <S%H4022><s%> of heaven <S%H8064><s%>, for the dew <S%H2919><s%>, And for the deep <S%H8415><s%> that coucheth beneath <S%H7257><s%>,
And for the precious <S%H4022><s%> things of the fruits <S%H8393><s%> of the sun <S%H8121><s%>, And for the precious things <S%H4022><s%> of the growth <S%H1645><s%> of the moons <S%H3391><s%>,
And for the chief things <S%H7218><s%> of the ancient <S%H6924><s%> mountains <S%H2042><s%>, And for the precious things <S%H4022><s%> of the everlasting <S%H5769><s%> hills <S%H1389><s%>,

And for the precious things <S%H4022><s%> of the earth <S%H776><s%> and the fulness <S%H4393><s%> thereof <S%H7522><s%>, And the good will of him that dwelt <S%H7931><s%> in the bush <S%H5572><s%>. Let the blessing come <S%H935><s%> upon the head <S%H7218><s%> of Joseph <S%H3130><s%>, And upon the crown of the head <S%H6936><s%> of him that was separate <S%H5139><s%> from his brethren <S%H251><s%>.

The firstling <S%H1060><s%> of his herd <S%H7794><s%>, majesty <S%H1926><s%> is his <S%H7161><s%>; And his horns are the horns <S%H7161><s%> of the wild-ox <S%H7214><s%>: With them he shall push <S%H5055><s%> the peoples <S%H5971><s%> all <S%H3162><s%> of them <S%H657><s%>, even the ends of the earth <S%H776><s%>: And they are the ten thousands <S%H7233><s%> of Ephraim <S%H669><s%>, And they are the thousands <S%H505><s%> of Manasseh <S%H4519><s%>.
And of Zebulun <S%H2074><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Rejoice <S%H8055><s%>, Zebulun <S%H2074><s%>, in thy going out <S%H3318><s%>; And <S%H3485><s%>, Issachar, in thy tents <S%H168><s%>.

They shall call <S%H7121><s%> the peoples <S%H5971><s%> unto the mountain <S%H2022><s%>; There shall they offer <S%H2076><s%> sacrifices <S%H2077><s%> of righteousness <S%H6664><s%>: For they shall suck <S%H3243><s%> the abundance <S%H8228><s%> of the seas <S%H3220><s%>, And the hidden <S%H2934><s%> treasures <S%H8226><s%> of the sand <S%H2344><s%>.

And of Gad <S%H1410><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Blessed <S%H1288><s%> be he that enlargeth <S%H7337><s%> Gad <S%H1410><s%>: He dwelleth <S%H7931><s%> as a lioness <S%H3833><s%>, And teareth <S%H2963><s%> the arm <S%H2220><s%>, yea <S%H637><s%>, the crown of the head <S%H6936><s%>.

And he provided <S%H7200><s%> the first part <S%H7225><s%> for himself <S%H2710><s%>, For there was the lawgiver's portion <S%H2513><s%> reserved <S%H5603><s%>; And he came <S%H857><s%> with the heads <S%H7218><s%> of the people <S%H5971><s%>; He executed <S%H6213><s%> the righteousness <S%H6666><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, And his ordinances <S%H4941><s%> with Israel <S%H3478><s%>.
And of Dan <S%H1835><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Dan <S%H1835><s%> is a lion <S%H738><s%>'s whelp <S%H1482><s%>, That leapeth <S%H2187><s%> forth from Bashan <S%H1316><s%>.

And of Naphtali <S%H5321><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, O Naphtali <S%H5321><s%>, satisfied <S%H7649><s%> with favor <S%H7522><s%>, And full <S%H4392><s%> with the blessing <S%H1293><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, Possess <S%H3423><s%> thou the west <S%H3220><s%> and the south <S%H1864><s%>.

And of Asher <S%H836><s%> he said <S%H559><s%>, Blessed <S%H1288><s%> be Asher <S%H836><s%> with children <S%H1121><s%>; Let him be acceptable <S%H7521><s%> unto his brethren <S%H251><s%>, And let him dip <S%H2881><s%> his foot <S%H7272><s%> in oil <S%H8081><s%>.
Thy bars <S%H4515><s%> shall be iron <S%H1270><s%> and brass <S%H5178><s%>; And as thy days <S%H3117><s%>, so shall thy strength be <S%H1679><s%>.

There is none like unto God <S%H410><s%>, O Jeshurun <S%H3484><s%>, Who rideth <S%H7392><s%> upon the heavens <S%H8064><s%> for thy help <S%H5828><s%>, And in his excellency <S%H1346><s%> on the skies <S%H7834><s%>.

The eternal <S%H6924><s%> God <S%H430><s%> is thy dwelling-place <S%H4585><s%>, And underneath are the everlasting <S%H5769><s%> arms <S%H2220><s%>. And he thrust out <S%H1644><s%> the enemy <S%H341><s%> from before <S%H6440><s%> thee <S%H559><s%>, And said, Destroy <S%H8045><s%>.

And Israel <S%H3478><s%> dwelleth <S%H7931><s%> in safety <S%H983><s%>, The fountain <S%H5869><s%> of Jacob <S%H3290><s%> alone <S%H910><s%>, In a land <S%H776><s%> of grain <S%H1715><s%> and new wine <S%H8492><s%>; Yea <S%H8064><s%>, his heavens drop down <S%H6201><s%> dew <S%H2919><s%>.

Happy <S%H835><s%> art thou <S%H3478><s%>, O Israel: Who is like unto thee <S%H5971><s%>, a people saved <S%H3467><s%> by Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, The shield <S%H4043><s%> of thy help <S%H5828><s%>, And the sword <S%H2719><s%> of thy excellency <S%H1346><s%>! And thine enemies <S%H341><s%> shall submit <S%H3584><s%> themselves unto thee <S%H1869><s%>; And thou shalt tread upon their high places <S%H1116><s%>.
